data.description: Come enjoy everything North Gate in Keys Gate has to offer. This 4-bedroom home has so much to offer with one of the largest lots in the neighborhood. Home features beautiful high ceilings, brand new wood looking porcelain flooring, updated kitchen with SS appliances, cabinets, quartz counter tops, 2 car garage and plenty of parking in your expansive driveway. This is the perfect home for a large family. The community offers a wonderful heated pool, clubhouse, gym, game room, theater, and great recreational spaces including beautiful walking paths. 24hr Security at both the gated entrance as well as roaming throughout the day/night. Maintenance fees high speed internet, basic cable, all lawn care including backyard spaces, exterior painting of home every 7 years, and alarm system.
